title: Tenacious D - The Complete Masterworks 2 (2008)
description:
This 2 disc DVD - which gives fans over three hours of footage - features a one hour plus documentary, a full length LIVE concert filmed in 2007 at the sold-out Moore Theatre in Seattle, WA, several bonus extras including the band&#039;s incredible performance on the 2006 MTV Movie Awards, their performance of "Master Exploder" on The Late Night with Conan O&#039;Brien, an unforgettable performance of "The Metal" on Saturday Night Live, numerous Tenacious D videos and more!
